{"tid":1435663,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"比人強姦緊你會唔會讓一步？","createTime":"2019-08-09T06:08:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T08:54:04.000Z","uid":36184,"like":59,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c91b0091bfae234e920e07fa9c299506eda80263","tid":1435663,"uid":36184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:08:25.000Z","msg":"發夢比人強姦緊<br />\n我使用&ldquo;武力&rdquo;去抵抗<br />\n一開始圍觀嘅人話&ldquo;佢咁大支，你點反抗都冇用架&rdquo;<br />\n之後我踢佢頭，佢話暫緩強姦<br />\n我係要你唔好強姦我，唔係暫時唔姦<br />\n<br />\n所以我繼續使用&ldquo;武力&rdquo;<br />\n圍觀的人話&ldquo;佢呢一刻都冇插入黎，你做咩姐&rdquo;<br />\n我今次踢佢春袋，佢話壽終正寢<br />\n<br />\n開始有人話你讓一步 咁先有偈傾<br />\n你下下反抗到咁行 你叫強姦嗰位點算？<br />\n你而家仲用&ldquo;武力&rdquo;，偏離晒啦，點支持你呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n退讓一步 歇息一日<br />\n並不會令我地壯大聲勢<br />\n只會令強姦你嗰位有氣唞<br />\n<br />\n香港人唔係咁撚蠢<br />\n要做嘅一定要繼續做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfacaa0d12c09972edccf746140d31aff90c8b61","tid":1435663,"uid":34525,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:18:03.000Z","msg":"咁要剪佢賓周了"},{"pid":"fd6cae8ca8db2caba897db3da8fac8729e81ee6a","tid":1435663,"uid":282624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:18:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c17c15bce2fecb92190f8ecdbfe4d4f50d51db3","tid":1435663,"uid":281584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:57:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wS0PDYcWh8U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwS0PDYcWh8U&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzfUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=8d7949a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wS0PDYcWh8U</a><br />\n<br />\n衣家唔係勇武同和理非咁簡單<br />\n係主戰同主和嘅分别<br />\n我地要打嬴老共自己實現5大訴求<br />\n定係出賣部分自己,底線同要求退讓以換取短暫且虛假嘅和平<br />\n睇老共姿態咁强硬,0371,國教嘅收埸咁樣讓步比和理非?<br />\n香港人衣家係思想革命嘅決擇時刻, RED PILL or BLUE PILL"},{"pid":"56647ef0e6f7fbc499c3588c5535f9fcb8035207","tid":1435663,"uid":36184,"like"